{"word":"βάπτισμα","slug":"βάπτισμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βάπτισμα, ατος, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βαπτίζω\">βαπτίζω</a></el>] ‘ceremonial washing’, <b><i>plunging, dipping, water-rite, baptism</i> <a href='B:470 3:7'>Mt 3:7</a>; <a href='B:480 11:30'>Mk 11:30</a>; <a href='B:520 6:4'>Ro 6:4</a>; <a href='B:560 4:5'>Eph 4:5</a>;</b> <el>βαπτίζεσϑαι <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάπτισμα\">βάπτισμα</a></el> <i>undergo</i> <i>a baptism</i> <b><a href='B:490 7:29'>Lk 7:29</a>.</b> By extension, of martyrdom <b><a href='B:480 10:38'>Mk 10:38f</a>; <a href='B:490 12:50'>Lk 12:50</a>.</b> In wordplay <b><a href='B:670 3:21'>1 Pt 3:21</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βαπτίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βαπτισμός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}